description:
As God’s followers, how do we deal with violence?

This #short clip from the message, “Noah’s Noble Life Together with God” by Pastor Sam Neves https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lTwZ4akh8uU&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_n_2Dh95i_CuVORnFlRIk1&index=8, shows Noah’s dignity. There is no doubt that he was a man with a noble character. Even though Noah and his family were surrounded by violence, he was perfect in his generation. Amidst other people’s disbelief, he chose to walk with and stay connected with God.

God invites us to open our doors so that He can live within us as He lived with Noah. Watch the video to hear Pastor Sam Neves highlight how Noah lived his life with dignity amid violence and evil and what we can learn from it.
